            "title": "consultations",
            "paragraphs": [
                {
                    "content": "I will conduct a comprehensive initial evaluation over 75 minutes for adults and over two 60 minutes sessions for children/adolescents.",
                    "paragraphListType": ""
                },
                {
                    "content": "After our initial meeting, I might order labs and review other documentation, or speak to other people in your life or to schools. At the conclusion of the evaluation, I provide a comprehensive assessment and treatment plan recommendations.",
                    "paragraphListType": ""
                },
                {
                    "content": "We will establish a physician-patient relationship if we mutually agree that my practice is an appropriate place for your treatment. If this is not the case, I will provide you with an alternative referral.",
                    "paragraphListType": ""
                },
                {
                    "content": "A consultation is not a guarantee that I will be able to take the individual on as a patient.",
                    "paragraphListType": ""
                }
            ]
        },
